data.description: This stunning one-level home boasts two bedrooms, two bathrooms, and is ideally situated on the golf course. With spacious interiors and incredible views, it offers a perfect blend of comfort and natural beauty.Upgraded Double French Doors with Blinds 2019, New Roof 2018, New window's 2019, New AC 2023, Water Softener 2018, New Exterior Paint 2023 and a New Refrigerator 2022. This home is certainly move in ready with lot's of awsome upgrades. All measurements are estimates and the responsibility of the buyer to verify. sellers are available for a quick close. With an acceptable offer the seller will contribute of $4,785.00 to buy the rate down for the buyer.Ex: if the normal Rate is 7.25% then the buyer would get 6.25% for the first 2 years.
